</blockquote><br />\n宜家情況係佢見某樣產品多人買<br />\n就想出自己品牌賺多啲<br />\n點知就收哂皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賣平價好野變賣超平價垃圾<br />\n想唔執都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380346adf0f4d7efb1a980ac26811e41e0ad62ac","tid":352662,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題係759真係少左好多人,<br />\n附近既優品360超多人,<br />\n優品360係舖位炒家林XX開<br />\n759就係做實業既廠佬開</blockquote><br />\n百佳係地產佬李+x 開添<br />\n買野姐 邊間平咪去邊間囉"},{"pid":"adeb112551d74b7ac611303cfe1b0dd1f9e1ecd7","tid":352662,"uid":38775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>759仲未識醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170524/56732715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170524%2F56732715&d=uv%2Fnv99QntN2KdwFnr6w1DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2f27e4d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170524%2F56732715&h=a79dd0b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170524/56732715</a><br />\n<br />\n仲要攻大陸<br />\n蝕59</blockquote><br />\n好少見大陸人幫襯759<br />\n多數去晒360價真棧"},{"pid":"3f90ac417363f3b829cd0a930976b6dd6aa78d1a","tid":352662,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前759 做得起係買人地係日本既貨尾 / 就過期既零食<br />\n<br />\n而家做大左，如果仲賣日本野蝕得仲多<br />\n<br />\nbtw 賣大陸野仲咁撚貴，<br />\n應該呢2-3年就全線玩完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解其他賣日本外國野既鋪又做得掂得佢蝕錢?</blockquote><br />\n係囉<br />\n360啲貨邊度黎？？"},{"pid":"56ffcb14a579bbe94db62bc93125a47519ee68d8","tid":352662,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bloc